                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Transport and Communications, 14.10.2009]</p>
                <p>Norway will together with Denmark and Sweden have air services negotiations with Iraq on 26 – 27 October and with Turkey on 5 – 6 November 2009.  The negotiations with Turkey were originally scheduled for the end of June this year but have been pushed back to the beginning of November.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
